# AgentMail UI environment.
#
# For local dev with the Go backend running at :8080 and Vite at :5173,
# leave this unset — Vite's server.proxy in vite.config.ts handles /api → :8080
# with chunked-encoding streaming preserved (see the proxy configure() hook).
#
# For a deployed build where the Go backend is same-origin, leave this unset.
# For a deployed build where the backend is on a separate origin (e.g. a
# Cloudflare tunnel), set VITE_API_BASE_URL to the absolute URL (no trailing
# slash), e.g.:
#
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://agentmail.example.com
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=
